OL,3,COfficer who called in sick to go on
OL,4,Choliday to Turkey barred from policing
OL,6,FA police constable who reported in
OL,7,Fsick on the day he flew to Turkey for
OL,8,Fa week-long holiday would have been
OL,9,Fdismissed if still serving with the
OL,10,Fforce, a disciplinary hearing has
OL,11,Fruled.
OL,13,FThe Independent Office for Police
OL,14,FConduct (IOPC) said gross misconduct
OL,15,Fwas proven against ex-Pc Raja Khan,
OL,16,Fwho was confronted by waiting police
OL,17,Fwhen his return flight landed at
OL,18,FLondon Stansted Airport on October 11
OL,19,Flast year.
