OL,3,COfficer who called in sick to go on
OL,4,Choliday to Turkey barred from policing
OL,6,FThe misconduct finding against the
OL,7,Fformer constable was made by a panel
OL,8,Fchaired by Leicestershire's Chief
OL,9,FConstable last week, following a
OL,10,FLeicestershire Police investigation
OL,11,Fdirected by the IOPC.
OL,13,FMr Khan, who resigned from the force
OL,14,Fin February, breached standards of
OL,15,Fprofessional behaviour governing
OL,16,Fhonesty and integrity,
OL,17,Fconfidentiality, orders and
OL,18,Finstructions, and discreditable
OL,19,Fconduct, the panel found.
