OL,3,COfficer who called in sick to go on
OL,4,Choliday to Turkey barred from policing
OL,6,FIn a statement issued on Tuesday, the
OL,7,FIOPC said the inquiry into the officer
OL,8,Ffound that he reported in sick on
OL,9,FOctober 5 while on a rest day, two
OL,10,Fdays before his next shift.
OL,12,FEvidence also indicated that he flew
OL,13,Fout to Istanbul for a holiday the same
OL,14,Fevening.
