OL,3,COfficer who called in sick to go on
OL,4,Choliday to Turkey barred from policing
OL,6,FOn October 8 Pc Khan was contacted by
OL,7,Fhis line manager and replied by text,
OL,8,Fsaying he was too ill to work, and was
OL,9,Fgiven the out-of-hours number to call
OL,10,Fthe sickness line and sent guidance to
OL,11,Fcomplete a sickness form, the IOPC
OL,12,Fsaid.
OL,14,FHe then got a third party to access
OL,15,Fhis police laptop back at home, submit
OL,16,Fthe sickness form on his behalf and
OL,17,Fsend an email from his work address to
OL,18,Fthe line manager confirming this had
OL,19,Fall been done.
