OL,3,COfficer who called in sick to go on
OL,4,Choliday to Turkey barred from policing
OL,6,FCommenting after the hearing, IOPC
OL,7,Fdirector of operations Steve Noonan
OL,8,Fsaid: "Pc Khan's behaviour fell well
OL,9,Fbelow the standards expected of a
OL,10,Fpolice officer."
OL,12,F"He was dishonest about his absence
OL,13,Ffrom work and compounded that by
OL,14,Fallowing an unauthorised person to
OL,15,Faccess his police laptop."
OL,17,F"In doing so he failed to treat
OL,18,Fconfidential information with respect."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/6
