OL,6,F"Such conduct has no place in policing
OL,7,Fand he will now be placed on the
OL,8,Fbarred list preventing him from future
OL,9,Femployment with the service."
OL,11,FPc Khan was arrested and interviewed
OL,12,Fon October 16, but a decision was made
OL,13,Fnot to make a referral to the Crown
OL,14,FProsecution Service to consider
OL,15,Fcriminal charges against the officer.
